OL,3,CTrash tracker: Where does Birmingham's
OL,4,Crubbish actually end up?
OL,6,FWatch Charlotte Cross' full report
OL,7,Finto rubbish tracking on ITVX.
OL,9,FDo you know where your rubbish goes
OL,10,Fafter it's been collected?
OL,12,FIt's probably not a question many
OL,13,Fpeople have spent too much time
OL,14,Fconsidering - but as the strikes in
OL,15,FBirmingham enter their second year,
OL,16,Fand with the return of recycling still
OL,17,Fmonths away, there's more attention
OL,18,Fthan ever on what's happening with our
OL,19,Fbins.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
