OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773667699
OL,3,CTrash tracker: Where does Birmingham's
OL,4,Crubbish actually end up?
OL,6,FSo we decided to find out what happens
OL,7,Fafter the waste goes into the wagon.
OL,8,FOver the last few months, volunteers
OL,9,Fput 18 GPS trackers into their bins in
OL,10,Fnine different locations across the
OL,11,Fcity - from Sutton Coldfield to
OL,12,FSparkbrook, and from Kings Heath to
OL,13,Fthe city centre.
OL,15,FWhere they ended up was fascinating.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
