OL,3,CTrash tracker: Where does Birmingham's
OL,4,Crubbish actually end up?
OL,6,FCllr Majid Mahmood, the council's
OL,7,Fenvironment chief, told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral: "The deal that we have with
OL,9,Four waste service providers is one of
OL,10,Fthe most attractive deals that we have
OL,11,Ffor waste disposal anywhere across the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,F"We want to take less to the
OL,15,Fincinerator, and more for recycling,
OL,16,Fin order that people are able to care
OL,17,Ffor the environment."
OL,26,@pD@JOUvD@AOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
