OL,3,CTrash tracker: Where does Birmingham's
OL,4,Crubbish actually end up?
OL,6,FAnd recycling is a big part of the
OL,7,Fcouncil's new waste strategy. It
OL,8,Fincludes food waste collections, which
OL,9,Fbegan rolling out this week, and the
OL,10,Freturn of dry recycling in June. As
OL,11,Fpart of that plan, it had wanted
OL,12,Frecycling rates to reach 40% by this
OL,13,Fyear. But in the first six months of
OL,14,F2025, they were instead just a little
OL,15,Fover 13%.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
