PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773667699
OL,3,CTrash tracker: Where does Birmingham's
OL,4,Crubbish actually end up?
OL,6,FCllr Mahmood acknowledges these
OL,7,Ffigures are unacceptably poor - though
OL,8,Fhe insists the council is making
OL,9,Fprogress. "Over the last six months,
OL,10,Fthe recycling rate has actually
OL,11,Fincreased to about 16.5%.
OL,13,F"By bringing in food recycling, we
OL,14,Festimate that will increase the
OL,15,Frecycling rate to between 10 and 15%,
OL,16,Fon top of the 16%, and having the
OL,17,Fadditional recycling bin, which is a
OL,18,F188-litre bin for paper recycling, we
OL,19,Fexpect to get to a 50% recycling rate
OL,20,Fwithin the next few years."
OL,26,@qD@KOUuD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
