OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773667699
OL,3,CTrash tracker: Where does Birmingham's
OL,4,Crubbish actually end up?
OL,6,FBut environmental campaigners are
OL,7,Fsceptical. They argue that continuing
OL,8,Fto use the incinerator means it needs
OL,9,Fenough rubbish to burn - limiting the
OL,10,Fincentive for rubbish to recycled
OL,11,Finstead.
OL,13,F"They need rubbish. If we become
OL,14,Fsuccessful at recycling, they will not
OL,15,Fhave a business model," John Newson,
OL,16,Fthe waste and recycling lead at
OL,17,FBirmingham Friends of the Earth, told
OL,18,Fme.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
