OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773667699
OL,3,CTrash tracker: Where does Birmingham's
OL,4,Crubbish actually end up?
OL,6,F"We need proper consultation and a
OL,7,Fproper waste strategy, to get to where
OL,8,Fwe need to get to. Which I would say
OL,9,Fis to close the incinerator because it
OL,10,Fis kind of all or nothing. Either
OL,11,Fyou're burning everything in the
OL,12,Fbuilding, or you're burning nothing.
OL,14,F"You can't have a one day a week
OL,15,Fincinerator, or a two hours a day
OL,16,Fincinerator - you can't just switch it
OL,17,Fon and off like that."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
