OL,3,CTrash tracker: Where does Birmingham's
OL,4,Crubbish actually end up?
OL,6,FCllr Mahmood insisted there was no
OL,7,Fbaseline for the amount of rubbish the
OL,8,Fcouncil needs to provide. And the
OL,9,Fcouncil said the changes to waste
OL,10,Fservices in the city will go ahead as
OL,11,Fplanned from June - regardless of
OL,12,Fwhether or not the strikes are still
OL,13,Fongoing.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
